== 航机资料 ==
本次涉事的C-130运输机于1978年为[[美国空军|美国空军]]建造，{{Le|美国军用航空器序列号|United States military aircraft serial numbers|机尾编号}}77-0324、序号382-4776，但最后交付[[美国海军陆战队|美国海军陆战队]]用作[[空中加油机|空中加油机]]，序号BuNo 160628。本机曾在[[北卡罗来纳州|北卡罗来纳州]]和日本[[岩國市|岩国市]]的美军基地服役。<ref>{{Cite web|title=US Navy and US Marine Corps BuNos--Third Series (160007 to 163049)|url=http://www.joebaugher.com/navy_serials/thirdseries21.html|accessdate=2020-10-30|author=|date=|format=|work=joebaugher|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2010-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101031101646/http://joebaugher.com/navy_serials/thirdseries21.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Historial del KC-130R de la Fuerza Aérea de Chile accidentado -noticia defensa.com - Noticias Defensa defensa.com Chile|url=https://www.defensa.com/chile/historial-kc-130r-fuerza-aerea-chile-accidentado|accessdate=2020-10-30|date=2019-12-12|last=Defensa.com|work=Defensa.com|language=es|archive-date=2020-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200911152000/https://www.defensa.com/chile/historial-kc-130r-fuerza-aerea-chile-accidentado|dead-url=no}}</ref>2009年至2014年，本机于[[亚利桑那州|亚利桑那州]][[图森_(亚利桑那州)|图森]]的空军机库闲置，后被智利空军以700万美金买下，于2015年交付使用，编号990。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Chile's Defense & Military: Air Force Acquires 2 Surplus C-130 Planes from U.S.|url=http://chiledefense.blogspot.com/2015/02/air-force-acquires-2-surplus-c-130.html|accessdate=2020-10-30|author=|date=2015-02-07|last=Arancibia|first=J. C.|format=|work=Chile's Defense & Military|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2020-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200911164059/http://chiledefense.blogspot.com/2015/02/air-force-acquires-2-surplus-c-130.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 事故过程 ==
{{NoteUTC}}

涉事航机于2019年12月9日16:55离开中转地[[蓬塔阿雷纳斯|蓬塔阿雷纳斯]]，前往南极洲[[乔治王岛|乔治王岛]]执行每月任务，计划为当地的智利空军基地提供补给及检查当地的输油管线等设施。<ref name=":1" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=Chile combs Antarctic for missing plane with 38 aboard|url=https://apnews.com/article/5f0d39bb9988e8a464fddf36f57367d0|accessdate=2020-10-30|date=2019-12-10|work=AP NEWS|archive-date=2020-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030115625/https://apnews.com/article/5f0d39bb9988e8a464fddf36f57367d0|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Chile missing aeroplane: Antartica-bound plane with 38 passengers disappears|url=https://www.express.co.uk/news/world/1215140/chile-missing-aeroplane-flight-Hercules-C130-disappears-Antartica-death-news-latest-update|accessdate=2020-10-30|date=2019-12-10|last=Bull|first=Millie|work=Express.co.uk|language=en|archive-date=2020-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200911152421/https://www.express.co.uk/news/world/1215140/chile-missing-aeroplane-flight-Hercules-C130-disappears-Antartica-death-news-latest-update|dead-url=no}}</ref>机上共有38人，其中有21名乘客和17名机组人员。机组成员全为智利空军人员<ref>{{Cite web|title=Chilean Air Force plane presumed crashed on its way to Antarctica|url=https://www.cnn.com/2019/12/10/americas/chile-air-force-plane-missing-intl-hnk/index.html|accessdate=2020-10-30|author=|date=2019-12-10|last=CNN|first=Jessie Yeung, Taylor Barnes and Tara John|format=|work=CNN|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2020-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200423172140/https://www.cnn.com/2019/12/10/americas/chile-air-force-plane-missing-intl-hnk/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，乘客中有15名智利空军官兵和2名平民<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|title=Chile missing plane: No survivors, confirms air force chief|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-latin-america-50752686|newspaper=BBC News|date=2019-12-12|accessdate=2020-10-30|language=en-GB|archive-date=2020-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201010005212/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-latin-america-50752686|dead-url=no}}</ref>。塔台在21:13和航机失去联系。<ref name=":1" /><ref>{{Cite news|title=Chilean air force says missing plane with 38 onboard has crashed|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2019/dec/10/chile-plane-with-38-on-board-goes-missing-on-way-to-antarctica|newspaper=The Guardian|date=2019-12-10|accessdate=2020-10-30|issn=0261-3077|language=en-GB|last=Reuters|archive-date=2020-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027043646/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2019/dec/10/chile-plane-with-38-on-board-goes-missing-on-way-to-antarctica|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 搜救过程 ==
智利军方协同英国、美国、阿根廷、巴西和乌拉圭方面搜索失事飞机。两艘{{Le|智利海军|Chilean Navy}}[[护卫舰|护卫舰]]在[[以色列國防軍|以色列国防军]]9900部队的协助下，在飞机于雷达画面上消失的地点附近展开搜索。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Israeli military helped find remains of crashed Chilean plane near Antarctica|url=https://www.timesofisrael.com/israeli-military-helped-find-remains-of-crashed-chilean-plane-near-antarctica/|accessdate=2020-10-30|last=Bachner|first=Michael|work=www.timesofisrael.com|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200911170134/https://www.timesofisrael.com/israeli-military-helped-find-remains-of-crashed-chilean-plane-near-antarctica/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=עם עיניים ישראליות: כך אותרו שרידי המטוס ליד אנטרקטיקה|url=https://www.ynet.co.il/articles/0,7340,L-5642653,00.html|accessdate=2020-10-30|date=2019-12-14|work=ynet|language=he|archive-date=2020-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200128232712/https://www.ynet.co.il/articles/0,7340,L-5642653,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>因海况恶劣、能见度低，搜索过程受到阻碍。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Chile search teams battle adverse conditions in hunt for plane|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-latin-america-50743673|newspaper=BBC News|date=2019-12-11|accessdate=2020-10-30|language=en-GB|archive-date=2019-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191218192411/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-latin-america-50743673|dead-url=no}}</ref>

搜索开始一天后，在飞机失联地点31公里外找到了飞机残骸。[[巴西海軍|巴西海军]]极地科考船{{Le|马克西米诺海军上将号科考船|Brazilian research ship Almirante Maximiano|马克西米诺海军上将号}}发现了乘员的个人物品。<ref name=":0" />

12月12日，搜救人员确定了飞机坠毁的位置，其位于飞机失联地点外27公里。飞机的机身、主要部件和部分乘员遗体成功辨认。<ref name=":2" />智利空军总司令阿图罗·梅里诺·贝尼特斯证实机上无生还者。<ref name=":0" />

智利军方表示因找回的部件不足，事故原因可能永远都不会查明。飞机可能在飞行中或沉入海底后解体。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Chilean air force chief says cause of Antarctic plane crash may never be known|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2019/dec/22/chilean-air-force-chief-says-cause-of-antarctic-plane-crash-may-never-be-known|accessdate=2020-10-30|date=2019-12-22|last=Reuters|work=the Guardian|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201004061755/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2019/dec/22/chilean-air-force-chief-says-cause-of-antarctic-plane-crash-may-never-be-known|dead-url=no}}</ref>

